OL,5, When Emma Vaughan left for work after  
OL,6, turning off her tumble dryer, she had  
OL,7, no idea she would return to a blazing  
OL,8, fire.                                  
OL,10,FThe fire service told her this was the 
OL,11,Fthird fire in the area two weeks caused
OL,12,Fby a tumble dryer.                     
OL,14,FMs Vaughan, 49, from Denbigh, in       
OL,15,FDenbighshire, is to be married in two  
OL,16,Fweeks and said the community support   
OL,17,Fhas been "overwhelming".               
OL,19,FA product safety engineer said the lint
OL,20,Ffilter should be cleared regularly.    
